English version :

This is an other tiny little IF (Interactive Fiction or text based game)
created this time for Moiki's challenge :
https://moiki.fr

This ADF version contains an intro image and a module.
The image is based on a photo made by Andréanne Boucher (CC license). The
module, "Kind of Earth" from 5.50 ***, is available on Aminet.

This disk, compatible with Kickstart 1.3 and above, will launch PPShow for
the picture, BastyPlayer for the module and finally FrotzStdIO for the game
itself. Yes, Frotz can run on 1.3 in its "Standard Input Output" version !!

New for this game, you can now launch the game from the floppy without
booting on it. You can find an icon in the floppy for launching the game
directly.


Information for Kickstart 1.3 or 2.0 users : you must maximize the Shell
window before playing!

But, if you are a Frotz user, you can use it to launch "Fenetre.z5" directly,
on Kickstart 2+, MorphOS, AROS, AmigaOS 4 or any other operating system
with Frotz or another Inform interpreter (Android, iOS, Windows, Linux, 
MacOS, PSP, Kindle, Psion 5, etc.).


Good game !

